relatedProfiles.full_name: S I M R A N  B E J W A N I 👑

latestPosts.caption: Never thought that i would be writing this but it has been 15 days now and it still hasn’t gotten easier. You came as surprise for my birthday and i still remember i fell on the floor from excitement. You filled such joy in our lives my baccha. You were such a cuddlu polu polu shonu baby. This happened way sooner than anyone imagined but shaayad isme hee kuch bhala hoga. You lit up the entire room with your presence. Next life mein bhi wont leave you, i had to irritate you and kiss you and smell you and hold you and poke you so many more times abhi tasalli nahi hui hai. Ghar shaant hogaya hai without you. You will always always be our little motlu my candu my baby. Will take care of mumma,  angel and nani from your side. Ghar ka raja hai tu aur humesha rahega or like mom likes to say you are the man of the house. I know you are in a better place. Always in our hearts, our prayers and dreams and always around us.
